{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So when Hitler came, he was able to get to England, and she was the landlady now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's how they also could maintain the property.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And she was a very tough cookie.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, as I said, I mean, this was one flight up and below was the concierge, the caretaker-- the couple that saw to it that the heat was on and the hot water was running and the stairs were clean, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when she engaged that couple, she said, no children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I can't stand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I can't tolerate it-- no children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was a condition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, there was a lot of unemployment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I told you about the social circumstances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When I was a young person, there was a lot of discontent and unrest and poverty, and that, of course, helped dictate a good common promise, whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When Hitler came, this couple said, now we are going to get even with her, went to the party, and said, she is listening to foreign broadcasts.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This was punishable by [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] death and then some, I suppose, because by then, the war had broken out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Don't forget-- '39, the war broke out in Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By then, of course, we didn't live there anymore because after my father left, when he was released, he had to leave within 30 days.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He managed in the 30 days to get all our paintings, get the permission and the license and-- and the paintings packed in a lift van and the furniture, and my trousseau, and so on, so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the lift van was sealed, ready for transportation to the United States as soon as we were going to leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
